============================================
XBMC Mixcloud Plugin - jackyNIX
============================================

Current version: 0.4.0 beta
============================================

Features:
  - Browse
    - New
    - Hot
    - Popular
    - Categories
  - Search
    - Cloudcasts
    - Users
  - Url resolving (removing invalid streams)
  - Thumbnails (configurable download size)
  - History
    - Played cloudcasts
    - Search
============================================

Todo:
  - Foolproof error handling
